name: It's Worse (V)
Lore: 'Things went from bad to worse when Luke was attacked by a dianoga, a parasitic predator native to the planet Vodran.',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy a pit from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR At end of your deploy phase, target a non-frozen captive at a site; captive is released and relocated to a related pit you do not occupy. OR During an attack, cancel a just drawn weapon destiny.',
